{"tid":2058013,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"本地原創團隊－整動畫、整Game、係STEAM上架","createTime":"2020-06-10T00:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T05:48:48.000Z","uid":360426,"like":164,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"eba6a769f6a10c482e471e320aa639f44946bf73","tid":2058013,"uid":360426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:04:56.000Z","msg":"首先比我地既動畫trailer大家睇先～<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iaNM-51tCXg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiaNM-51tCXg&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=bde07680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iaNM-51tCXg</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，我地係Gamestry Lab，係全香港班底既Game＋動畫團隊。<br />\n呢幾日見到大家對於本地動畫同Game都非常支持同有興趣，<br />\n所以都想同大家交流多d，唔再單單埋頭苦幹咁做自己作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果過往幾年有去動漫展都有機會見過我地～<br />\n試玩過我地之前隻Game仲係勁初步勁簡陋時既版本。<br />\n其實我地本身都係幾個freelancer，<br />\n一邊做job維生，一邊做自己既動畫/遊戲作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機緣巧合之下，大前年開始合作想整一隻完成度高d既作品。<br />\n過程好多波折，嘗試過唔同方法去搵開發資金等都唔成功。<br />\n係香港係非常難搵到投資，而遊戲眾籌亦都係吃力不討好既事，<br />\n最後唯有自己谷住道氣頂住，繼續一路做job一路開發，<br />\n後尾都好彩申請到d資助完成條動畫，做到少少宣傳，<br />\n直至舊年early access完成後上架STEAM<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地本身做既game係同班friend一齊玩hehehaha既party game，<br />\n但係舊年下半年early access完成後我地都爭扎左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為始終大家都未必太有心情同時間去買同玩呢類型既遊戲。<br />\n變左我地只好一路默默開發，慢慢完善好隻game先，<br />\n一直都好怕係個錯既時間做宣傳，令到大家會有hard feeling<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係呢兩日見到大家都好熱烈討論本地遊戲同動畫製作，<br />\n所以想借住呢個機會上一上水，比大家認識下我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信香港仲有好多好多為自己作品努力打拼緊既朋友，<br />\n特別係做緊原創既團隊，係香港係非常難生存(唔好話要賺錢)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知有好多高水準作品都只係得圈內人認識，好少得到大眾既支持同欣賞。<br />\n咁樣慢慢令到資源同機會都好難留係本地圈子入面，慢慢越做越縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n若果大家都認同香港需要有更多本地既創作，<br />\n大家既支持係非常非常非常緊要！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人撐本地創作，可以吸引到更多討論同迴響，<br />\n市場就會比更多機會同資源香港既創作者，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自然就可以令到香港既作品同創作人繼續發展，越做越多越好！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講左咁多，<br />\n當然想大家都可以支持下我地隻STEAM game －－ <br />\nBalance Breakers <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://steampowered.com/app/1069750/Balance_Breakers/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsteampowered.com%2Fapp%2F1069750%2FBalance_Breakers%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=c903bb53\" target=\"_blank\">http://steampowered.com/app/1069750/Balance_Breakers/</a><br />\n<br />\n接近100% Made in Hong Kong (有少少音樂係日本朋友幫手整)<br />\n而家更新仲做緊特價優惠，未有fd一齊玩都可以睇住入面既Animation全片先～<br />\nWishlist同直接買都可以幫到我地，買左既玩完都比返個評價我地，<br />\n呢幾個動作都可以令到隻game係STEAM度增加曝光，提高銷量～<br />\n大家既支持，可以幫到我地團隊繼續營運，<br />\n令到我地可以繼續努力創作高質素作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外仲可以like埋我地facebook page：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/GamestryLab/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FGamestryLab%2F&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=667384d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/GamestryLab/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係我地團隊頂唔順之前，都一定會繼續努力開發同生存落去，<br />\n如果有咩問題，歡迎係度問或者facebook PM我地，<br />\n答到既我地都會盡力回答～<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n好多人問幾時有Online？<br />\n整緊，下個Update就係會有Online，等多一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以係STEAM度Wishlist住先，下次Update再優惠比大家買！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1756c6eeaa826ecad6b0bf2f3bbea44724bb443","tid":2058013,"uid":287747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"好高質 要支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3522cc844897a636c5c2f28a79206e9d785a52","tid":2058013,"uid":137088,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:11:19.000Z","msg":"支持 淨係睇左條片<br />\n<br />\n場景好花 唔係好睇到發生緊咩咩事<br />\n特別係綠色格仔個景<br />\n建議攪下d配色"},{"pid":"c0fb791c27482e3f244805fc6595d128783d21d8","tid":2058013,"uid":167802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:13:41.000Z","msg":"癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8f4d690f60e9c1460b48354bd59476983dcf8a","tid":2058013,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可惜我唔鍾意玩哩類game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過都支持下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7ccfa28e0607061282afb7ad96379292f88257","tid":2058013,"uid":88139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:21:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80632a0a62adf158ec2fd2986af9e7eb7d80b400","tid":2058013,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:29:34.000Z","msg":"動漫節試玩過 幫推"},{"pid":"ff6693c547cbb385a37ad6503089ef1fa69f82ed","tid":2058013,"uid":80936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T00:56:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"39ed52672815311b1dca9351487fb4cdef780ad6","tid":2058013,"uid":