e":"2020-06-10T01:57:47.000Z","msg":"一班人玩應該好正, 有D似好耐以前隻power stone.<br />\n不過暫時無online應該都係買黎擺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加住wishlist 先"},{"pid":"9fabda36ba6d7274a9ee21f7b48c186a7dd2b5c5","tid":2058013,"uid":30831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T01:58:18.000Z","msg":"睇得出勁有心機整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔係pvp fan."},{"pid":"e45e29e610e7a38854a354a529b5774d8104b15e","tid":2058013,"uid":360426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c5c6372eeed9685112c05f94f5dd7105d150888","tid":2058013,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T01:29:22.000Z","msg":"隻game睇落幾街機feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多口問句，有冇政府錢注資？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:01:47.000Z","msg":"有參加過d支援計劃，<br />\n叫做可以吊住我地團隊條命咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係政府錢都係杯水車薪，<br />\n如果要計開發費就一定無可能cover到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59a526dd212ead1df6ba09d5bc96a98c5d72162","tid":2058013,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26edbcbe071fa115c6876ede5b6cceb26040ad7d","tid":2058013,"uid":65187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:06:06.000Z","msg":"動漫節試玩過 幾得意<br />\n啲人幾nice 推"},{"pid":"759fa0b994f11b23bf2e4feb1c6f1bba001c83ae","tid":2058013,"uid":78892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"580f71bdbe777212cb2fe3bf84756de503200e4a","tid":2058013,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T02:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac